OL,4,G2325FBehind Bars: World's Toughest
OL,5,     FPrisons
OL,6,     GIn the Philippines CIW,
OL,7,     Gcorrection officers risk their
OL,8,     Glives to deal with more than 3000
OL,9,     Gprisoners, especially during the
OL,10,     Gday, when over 1000 prisoners are
OL,11,     Gnot locked up.
OL,12,G0030FBehind Bars: World's Toughest
OL,13,     FPrisons
OL,14,     GNew Bilibid Prison is one of the
OL,15,     Gmost notorious prisons in the
OL,16,     GPhilippines. Originally designed
OL,17,     Gto hold 1500 offenders, there are
OL,18,     Gnow more than 8000 incarcerated
OL,19,     Gthere.
